sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant A as API controller
  participant S as Ledger service
  participant U as Core use case
  participant W as Unit of work
  participant R as Repository adapters

  C->>A: POST ledger entries
  A->>S: normalized command
  S->>U: execute
  U->>W: begin transaction
  U->>R: persist transaction and entries
  U->>W: commit
  U-->>A: result
  A-->>C: response
